          <p class='first-para'>
            I am entirely in your Lordships' hands, but I notice that it is 7.26 p.m. I think this is a convenient moment for the Committee to adjourn until Wednesday at 3.30 p.m.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
